  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110105864723\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110105864723\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--StartFragment--> \r\n<p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8212cacea8ba8935.jpg\" width=\"181\" height=\"181\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110330_46/isuhani_13014649437906ubda_JPEG/%B1%B8%C3%EBd.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A2D22A13')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8212cacea8ba8935.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">●구취(입 냄새)의 종류는?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><?xml:namespace prefix = v ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" /><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"></v:stroke><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"></v:path><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"></o:lock></v:shapetype><v:shape style=\"POSITION: absolute; MARGIN-TOP: 12.39pt; WIDTH: 133.1pt; HEIGHT: 133.1pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 315.73pt; v-text-anchor: top; mso-position-vertical-relative: line; mso-position-vertical: absolute; mso-position-horizontal-relative: text; mso-position-horizontal: absolute\" id=\"_x116305880\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"><!-- localfile --><v></v:imagedata><?xml:namespace prefix = w ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" /><w:wrap type=\"square\"></w:wrap></v:shape><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">입 안에서 풍겨 나오는 냄새와 숨을 쉴 때 호흡을 통해 나는 냄새가 있어요.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\" lang=\"EN-US\">- 입 안에서 나는 냄새 :</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\" lang=\"EN-US\"> 주로 박테리아가 만들어 내는 냄새로 입을 벌리고 대화를 할 때 느껴지며 입이 마르거나 자극적인 음식을 먹은 후 심해져요.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\" lang=\"EN-US\">- 숨을 쉴 때 나는 냄새 :</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\" lang=\"EN-US\"> 호기성 구취라 하고 대부분 위,장,간 등의 소화기관과 폐,기관지에서 발생하죠.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a1874e6bc3cbe2a9.jpg\" width=\"119\" height=\"119\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110330_289/isuhani_1301464827149A5lPS_JPEG/%B1%B8%C3%EB.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A2D22A13')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a1874e6bc3cbe2a9.jpg\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">●입 냄새는 치료 될 수 있나요?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">구취(입 냄새)로 오랜 시간 고생했던 분들은 자신의 입 냄새를 없앨 수 없다고 생각하시는 경우가 많습니다. 치과치료 열심히 받고, 양치질도 열심히 해봐도 해결되지 않았기 때문이죠. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">입 냄새는 한약 치료를 통해 오장 육부의 근본적 원인을 치료하면서 구강 환경을 개선하면 치료될 수 있어요. 실제 치료되신 분들도 많구요. 다만, 환자에 따라 원인 장부가 다르기 때문에 진료가 필요하죠.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8a299213f5cb9cfe.jpg\" width=\"120\" height=\"101\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110330_107/isuhani_13014649623013XK75_JPEG/%B1%B8%C3%EB_%C7%E2%B1%E2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A2D22A13')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8a299213f5cb9cfe.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\">\r\n</p><p class=\"바탕글\"><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"></v:stroke><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"></v:path><o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"></o:lock></v:shapetype><v:shape style=\"POSITION: absolute; MARGIN-TOP: 28.26pt; WIDTH: 132.74pt; HEIGHT: 111.5pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 320.8pt; v-text-anchor: top; mso-position-vertical-relative: line; mso-position-vertical: absolute; mso-position-horizontal-relative: text; mso-position-horizontal: absolute\" id=\"_x116406016\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"><!-- localfile --><v></v:imagedata><w:wrap type=\"square\"></w:wrap></v:shape><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">●왜 한방 치료를 해야 하나요?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">입 냄새는 단순히 한가지 원인 때문에 발생하는 것이 아니라 </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #ff0000; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">입 마름, 설태, 소화불량, 식도 역류, 열(熱), 피로</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\" lang=\"EN-US\"> 등의 증상이 복합적으로 작용을 해서 발생 하는 것이므로 오장육부의 전반적 문제를 포괄해서 해결할 수 있는 한방치료가 가장 효과적인 방법입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">주로 비위의 열을 식혀주는 </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #0066ff; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">한약치료</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">를 위주로 하게 되며, </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: #0066ff; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">주 2회 침치료</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">를 병행하면 더욱 효과적입니다. </span></p><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"></v:stroke><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"></v:path><o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"></o:lock></v:shapetype>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><v:shape style=\"POSITION: absolute; MARGIN-TOP: 34.71pt; WIDTH: 18.48pt; HEIGHT: 17.12pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 369.79pt; v-text-anchor: top; mso-position-vertical-relative: line; mso-position-vertical: absolute; mso-position-horizontal-relative: text; mso-position-horizontal: absolute\" id=\"_x116420720\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"><!-- localfile --><v></v:imagedata></v:shape><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\">치료는 가벼운 경우 1개월이면 호전을 보이고, 중한 경우 상태에 따라서 기간이 길어지게 됩니다. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110330_133/isuhani_13014649753293hIII_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20110330_133/isuhani_13014649753293hIII_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A2D22A13')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20110330_133/isuhani_13014649753293hIII_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right\" class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right\" class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
